        <h4>Welcome to the wonderful world of Musical Magic!</h4>
        <p>Whether it's classical or prog rock; the world runs on music. So why wouldn't we want to harness it into our magical casting as well? If you want to make the world a more wonderful place, then becoming a Bard is for you.</p>
        <p>Bards are rarely quiet and solitary. They're an integral part of any party, helping others around feel inspired and better than they did before.<p>
        <h5>In this class you will learn:</h5>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <h5>Magical Inspiration</h5>
                <p>Our first lesson will be how to give inspiration to those around you, improving their performances above and beyond what they can do themselves.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <h5>Musical Spellcasting</h5>
                <p>We will also cover some basic spellcasting, as well as the ability to use your music as a focus for your magical casting</p>
                <p>An example of the spells we cover are:</p>
